review_title: Definitely a must have if you take your dog anywhere
reviews: Great to have on the go so you always have water for your pup. So lightweight that my puppy has learned to grab it by the carabiner and drag it but he's just a puppy so still has to learn haha.

review_title: This will be the only glove I buy going forward!
reviews: Amazing gloves! I had bought a glove at a golf store with limited stock during the pandemic and it had torn right away - this beats it by far in quality and fit. I was skeptical about the one-size-fits-all idea but the compression works very well and I feel like the glove was fit exactly to my hand, no issue with the stretch. The velcro is very secure, and the material is supportive but breathable where it needs to be - a good combo of the leather/mesh.

Bought this as a bday present for my niece and she absolutely loved it. The material is thicker than your standard canvas backpack, almost feels like a neoprene material. Colours are great and vibrant. If I had to be critical I would say the zipper is tougher for a kid to do up themselves due to the material but she was able to do it when I was helping her by holding it taut. Would definitely buy again, got huge style points from both kid and parents.

review_title: So easy to pop out because of silicone bottoms!
reviews: Wanted an ice tray with a lid as my freezer space is limited and I was tired of using open trays and spilling. These are great, they work like the reusable lunch containers I have with snap locks on every side. I haven't tried to use it tilted or on its side so I haven't tested any spillage but it seems to hold everything in well. The silicone bottoms are my favorite part as they make it super easy to get the cubes out as you can pop them up nicely. I usually make a bunch of ice and then store it in a separate container so I haven't tested the ice after its sat in this container for more than a few hours like a couple other reviews have stated.

review_title: Good quality for a cheap shirt
reviews: Purchased this to add an iron on image for a friend. Fits as expected and great quality.

review_title: Cute jewelry tray that fits a lot of pieces
reviews: Purchased this for my nightstand so I could have a place to put my everyday jewelry that I take off before bed. It's cute and very wide, not like other dishes I've seen where you can only fit a couple pieces. If I had to be nitpicky the one thing I don't like is that the letter is not straight but that's for my OCD mind to battle with! Haha. Overall would buy again.

Purchased this because it had a dual function of charging and aux capability. Unfortunately the dual stopped working within the first 3 times of using this. I find that the aux works but then when I go to plug the charger in it just stops completely so I only use this as an aux adapter in my car. Very disappointed as I wanted to be able to use both.
Purchased this before we went to Cuba. It was very easy to pack (rolled it up) and it kept its shape very well. Used it on the beach every day and it is nice and light. Would definitely recommend.

I was very surprised at how well this works. I often wake up to the light before the alarm even goes off. Only had it for a week so I am still playing with the functions and haven't quite worked it out. I like that it has 2 alarm options, a variety of sounds, and several light levels. I suffer from SAD and that on top of the spring time change does wonders on me but this is helping tremendously.

Love that this is 2 pieces, actually looks like one when you wear it. Wore this on a beach trip and it was so comfortable. I'm not a fan of my midriff and this hides it perfectly and stylishly. Would definitely buy again!

Purchased this to be able to charge my phone and play music at the same time. It worked for the first week maybe and then completely stopped. I can only use it for music now, if I try to plug the power cord in it stops working. Will not buy again. Haven't found a dual adapter for usb c that works yet, disappointing.

review_title: Perfect for a Christmas gift or personalized family ornaments on your tree
reviews: These turned out great! Received them very quickly and the quality is quite good. I was worried about the names, especially a couple long names with 8-9 letters, but they came out very nicely and legibly. Purchased this set for my boyfriend's family and will be using these in place of gift name tags this year!

review_title: Great value and cheap, simple alternative to Fitbit
reviews: Great value. I wanted a simple step counter without the frills or high price of a Fitbit. This works great. Battery life is very good - I get about a week and a half per charge. The one thing I am not crazy about is that I'm not confident in its accuracy for step counting - I tested it by getting up and walking around my office (approx. 40 steps) and the number did not change. The other feature I like is that you can set alarms on it - I use this in the morning to keep me on track with leaving the house on time, and at work to remind me to take lunch and give me a heads up about 15min before it is home time. Would definitely buy again and recommend to someone who wants a simple alternative.

Great mat - I use this for on the go (roll my straightener up in it and secure with rubber bands). This allows me to use my straightener anywhere - on the bed, on my dresser, on my vanity, etc. Would definitely recommend as both a heat barrier and travel companion.

Purchased as a gift for my boyfriend and he loves it! He has always had issues sleeping and his blanket has improved the quality of his sleep tenfold. It is lightweight and stays very cool - I was worried about this as he has trouble with staying cool overnight but it does not overheat at all.

I actually use this for earrings as I have tons of stud earrings and nowhere to properly store. This was a great solution and also a great display tool! I can scan quickly and grab whatever pair I want.

I've always had trouble storing jewelry in my overnight bag - this is a great solution! Only comment is the same as I've seen from others where certain rings will not fit if they have a stone or if they sit higher than the band. I've been able to turn the rings to make them fit which works for now. Definitely would recommend as it has been perfect for the past weddings I've attended where we had to get ready at the hotel and bring several options!

Bought this for my boyfriend so he has is own - I have the original one already that he kept stealing. The only think I don't like about this is that it is a velvety material. My original one is a fabric that is easier to clean.

review_title: Great wedding gift - the couple loved it!
reviews: Such a great wedding gift! We gave it to our friends and they used it the next morning after the wedding. The customization was great. It also arrived faster than expected. Will definitely buy again!

review_title: Great option to those without A/C
reviews: Works very well! Don't have A/C in my bedroom so this was a decent solution. Been using it the past week and it's better at night in terms of getting the temp down. Really like that it has a thermostat as I use it to monitor the room. Only comment is that I wish it had some sort of directions in terms of what's the most useful setting for the airflow (both in vs in out vs both out) as I've had to play with it and not perfected yet.

review_title: Great length and perfect for many occasions
reviews: Love this! So easy to throw on, great length, and perfect for work or going out! Will buy again, kind of want 3 of these in my closet!
My boyfriend and I have different phones (iphone vs android) so this is very useful for us in the car, as well as on the go. He has one clipped to his keys. Its an adapter and it works.
Once you go 10FT you never go back.
Bought this for my boyfriend's new phone and he loves it. Very durable and not too bulky.

Touch screen works well through the case - I was a little worried it would be finicky but it was fine. Took this kayaking and was just a safeguard for my phone and kept my mind at peace. Did not try the floating feature but lanyard that comes with it is useful.

My boyfriend and I both purchased a pair of these for a camping trip. These were perfect for kayaking where you had to briefly wade into the water, and they drained very well/dried well overnight. The convenience of throwing these on and not having to change or remove shoes from the car to the water was very helpful. As others have mentioned these do not have padding underneath so are not ideal for hiking as you can feel everything you step on! Overall, would definitely buy again. We're keeping these for future use!
Bought this as part of my boyfriend's christmas gift and he loves it. Comes with nice case. Great for him to use for work (sales rep) in a professional setting.

review_title: Bought it for my car aux system
reviews: Works well. Great to be able to have headphones plugged in as well as charge at the same time.

I've used this brand for several past phones and have never had a problem with wet mount applications. I tried to apply this twice in two consecutive days, both waiting overnight for each application to dry. Both times it failed and the layer 2 did not separate from the film protector itself which caused dust to get in and cause bubbles. Also it is definitely not fingerprint reducing as I am having the same problem as my original glass protector. Will not buy again - guess I have to wait for more vendors to make something for this phone.
Fast charging is great on this
Have gotten many compliments on it. Hung it up above my bed.
Worked great for my transition from my old phone micro usb to my new phone usb c. Makes the connection point a little longer but overall works great.

review_title: Love this for personal reflection. Would also be a great gift.
reviews: My friend and boyfriend saw this in my room and both loved it. I put the day of the week in as well as a prompt for myself in case I forget a day. Overall, hilarious as going even a week back you won't remember what you put in. Can't wait to do it over a year and see what my answers will be on the next go around!

review_title: Was a gift - they loved it
reviews: Gave it to my boyfriend for his birthday and he loved it. Warm fleece on the inside makes it perfect for winter.
It's exactly as it describes. Clean after every shower to keep it pristine. I'm pretty grossed out by this stuff but its a great tool considering it prevents the even grosser task of drain cleaning.
Perfect size for on the go. Love having this travelling for work, commuting, or even around the house. Sometimes takes a while to charge, but understandable as it holds 3-4x the charge.

review_title: Love it. Way better than your run of the mill Android box or Apple TV.
reviews: Love this thing! New, fresh, fast, and great quality display. Loaded all my regular apps and they work great (Netflix, Amazon Prime Video, Crave, Youtube, Kodi). One flaw I'd say is that as it's on the amazon platform there are apps (ex. TSN App in Canada) that are not compatible yet. Hopefully those come soon.

review_title: Love this - received in good condition and keeps everything ...
reviews: Love this - received in good condition and keeps everything very organized. My only qualms are that the lock doesn't work but that's more decorative for me anyways and the base takes up a bit of room but it does look good regardless. Would buy again.

review_title: This is great! I commute about 3 hours a day and ...
reviews: This is great! I commute about 3 hours a day and keep this in my purse in case I run out of juice so its become very handy. At full battery this will last weeks and multiple recharges of my phone. Also not bad charging 2 things at a time. It's a bit bigger than normal ones but I don't mind for the convenience that this lasts a while. Would buy again.

review_title: This does give you support but I still feel like my face is smushed against it every time
reviews: This does give you support but I still feel like my face is smushed against it every time. The Velcro is loud so I try to adjust only at the beginning and end of flights. Not sure I'd purchase again.

review_title: ... a beauty blender to this silicone pad and I like this better
reviews: I went from a beauty blender to this silicone pad and I like this better. It's a bit of an adjustment in terms of the dabbing technique but you get the hang of it. It uses less makeup as it all goes on your face instead of being soaked into the sponge. Very easy to clean, which is my favorite part about it. Would definitely buy again.
Not bad for a cheap straightener. Heats up very quickly.

review_title: Good quality image though and I've gotten a lot of ...
reviews: Its basically just a clear case with a printed design of the black/gold marble pattern on the back panel, so it's not a solid coloured case if that's what you were expecting. Good quality image though and I've gotten a lot of compliments on it already. Would buy again.

review_title: It's really only good for Netflix or Youtube - both of which I ...
reviews: Returning this. It's really only good for Netflix or Youtube - both of which I can do on my Xbox so it makes this irrelevant. Most of the Roku content is not available yet, so it was tough to find anything. Plus the remote was very inconsistent - it unpaired constantly. The app was alright though, and I used it on my phone as a remote. I'm going with an Android box instead.

review_title: Bought this so I could use Bluetooth functions and was hoping it was a better option for car phone calls
reviews: Returned this - I have an AUX port in my car but no Bluetooth. Bought this so I could use Bluetooth functions and was hoping it was a better option for car phone calls. It reduced the quality of the sound by about 50% plus lots of static. I'm sticking to the AUX.
Returning this - max weight is only 100 grams so it was tough to do anything.
Great deal at that price. Using these as a supplement to my main brush set, always good to have extras.

review_title: Not bad - no odour at all when it was unrolled ...
reviews: Not bad - no odour at all when it was unrolled and only took a day to settle. A bit more firm than I realized, but may also be because it's winter. Hoping it loosens a little.
Works well - used it to hook up my MacBook to the TV.
Decent brushes for the money - just use them as supplements for one of my palettes.
He sits on my desk at work so proudly.

review_title: Great mount - been using it for a while to ...
reviews: Great mount - been using it for a while to keep myself hands free while driving. Clamps well, no risk of it falling.

review_title: Great cord, lightweight and thin head which lets it ...
reviews: Great cord, lightweight and thin head which lets it fit into my phone while my case is on. Quality is great as well.

Bought this as a gift for my mother's birthday in Feb 2014. She liked it a lot.
Quality of product was good - will update if anything changes.
No one buys CD's anymore, but this one is definitely worth your money. Wish I could've seen them live last year!
Got this for my brother's LG Optimus Net phone. Had trouble finding cases for his phone but this one was pretty decent, and fits well. Has correct cut-outs. Would recommend.

Like others, I had initially written a good review as it had worked perfectly when received. At the 6 month mark, it just stopped working without reason. Seller has not gotten back to me despite several attempts to reconcile the matter. DO NOT BUY for long term use. Now I have to figure out if buying the Apple one is worth it.

review_title: Exactly what I needed and ordered
reviews: This battery works great - it is exactly what I needed and the capacity is right up to standard. Works wonderfully.
